Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:51.97,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur\be1}You act tough, and never show any tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.06,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}hontou wa kowai kuseni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.06,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}But I know you're scared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:03.56,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}taisetsu na mono wo ushinawa nu you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:03.56,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}You keep running so you don't lose what's important
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.98,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}hisshi de hashirinukete kita
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.98,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}We've always survived through the long night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:15.55,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}itsu datte nagai yoru wo futari de norikoeta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:15.55,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}I'll always be by your side
