Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:29.21,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}nakijakuru kodomo no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:29.21,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}you're just like a crying child
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:35.69,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}tatoe asu ga mienaku natte mo susumu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.11,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}We'll keep moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:35.69,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}even though we don't know what tomorrow will bring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:41.53,JPN OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}natsu no sora miagete sakenda
